# Move the major files to SSD for better loading
 - **SSD Path:** 
 `/home/archsean/Games/CyberPunk2077/archive/pc/content/` - 
 **HDD Path:** 
 `/mnt/sdb4/SteamLibrary/steamapps/common/Cyberpunk 2077/archive/pc/content/` 
 **Commands used:** 
 #  Create SSD target 
 mkdir -p /home/archsean/Games/CyberPunk2077/archive/pc/content/ 
 # 2. Move high-impact files to SSD (Textures/Geometry) 
 mv -v basegame_3_nightcity* basegame_4_appearance.archive basegame_4_gamedata.archive basegame_1_engine.archive /home/archsean/Games/CyberPunk2077/archive/pc/content/ # 3. Create Symlinks back to HDD Steam folder 
 # Change Directory
 cd "/mnt/sdb4/SteamLibrary/steamapps/common/Cyberpunk 2077/archive/pc/content/" 
# Link files via symlinks
ln -s /home/archsean/Games/CyberPunk2077/archive/pc/content/basegame_3_nightcity* . 
ln -s /home/archsean/Games/CyberPunk2077/archive/pc/content/basegame_4_appearance.archive . 
ln -s /home/archsean/Games/CyberPunk2077/archive/pc/content/basegame_4_gamedata.archive . 
ln -s /home/archsean/Games/CyberPunk2077/archive/pc/content/basegame_1_engine.archive .
 
Launch Settings : '%command% --launcher-skip -skipStartScreen'
Proton Version : GE(Glorious Eggroll)

Steam  - > Settings -> General -> Language -> Japanese (game will instALL Japanese audio and language files) :
Next - Change the menus back to English :
- **Settings Path:** Main Menu > 3rd from bottom > 3rd icon from right. -Language (言語)  
- **Top Dropdown (Interface / インターフェース):** Click and scroll until you find **English**. (This fixes all menus/text).
- **Middle Dropdown (Subtitles / 字幕):** Set to **English**.
- **Bottom Dropdown (Audio / 音声):** Keep this as **Japanese**.
